termination_clause.text:
Termination.

10.1 This Development Agreement will begin on the Effective Date and continue for four (4) years unless earlier terminated pursuant to Section  10.2, or unless the parties extend the term by mutual written Development Agreement ("Term").  10.2 Either Party may terminate this Development Agreement by giving written notice to the other Party, (a)in the event the other Party's  bankruptcy, insolvency, or the filing of a petition therefore; and (b) the other Party materially defaults in the performance of its obligations  hereunder. This Development Agreement shall also terminate upon mutual written agreement by the Parties.
